\/laylat-al-qadar-thousand-months\/","url_meta":{"origin":20755,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Laylat al-Qadar better than a thousand months","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 30, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said when the month of Ramadan began, \u201cVerily, this month has presented itself to you. There is a night within it that is better than a thousand months. Whoever is deprived of it has been deprived\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15513,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/29\/ramadan-knowledge-night-decree\/","url_meta":{"origin":20755,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Knowledge of Laylat al-Qadr removed by insults","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 29, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, came out to inform people about the Night of Decree\u00a0in Ramadan, but two Muslim men were insulting each other. The Prophet said, \u201cVerily, I have come out to tell you about the Night of Decree, but\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3705,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/18\/siyam-salat-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":20755,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Reward of fasting and praying in Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 18, 2012","format